### 6.3 Level of Detail (LOD)

```typescript
// Good: Use LOD for complex objects
import { LOD } from 'three'

const lod = new LOD()

// High detail - close up
const highDetail = new Mesh(
  new SphereGeometry(1, 32, 32),
  material
)
lod.addLevel(highDetail, 0)

// Medium detail - mid range
